```plantuml
@startuml inovex_scrumlr.io

actor User
participant "Frontend (React)" as Frontend
participant "API Router" as Router
participant "Board Service" as BoardService
participant "Database (bun ORM)" as Database
participant "Realtime Service (NATS/Redis)" as Realtime

User -> Frontend: Creates new board
Frontend -> Router: POST /boards (with board details)
Router -> BoardService: createBoard(boardData)
BoardService -> Database: Save board data
Database --> BoardService: Saved board
BoardService --> Router: Board DTO
Router --> Frontend: Board created response
Frontend -> Realtime: Subscribe to board updates (WebSocket)
Realtime --> Frontend: Acknowledge subscription

User -> Frontend: Adds note to board
Frontend -> Router: POST /boards/{id}/notes (with note data)
Router -> BoardService: addNote(boardId, noteData)
BoardService -> Database: Save note
Database --> BoardService: Saved note
BoardService -> Realtime: Publish noteAdded event
Realtime -> Frontend: Broadcast noteAdded (via WebSocket)
Frontend -> Frontend: Update local state (Redux)

User -> Frontend: Votes on note
Frontend -> Router: PUT /boards/{id}/notes/{noteId}/vote
Router -> BoardService: voteOnNote(boardId, noteId, userId)
BoardService -> Database: Update note votes
Database --> BoardService: Updated note
BoardService -> Realtime: Publish noteUpdated event
Realtime -> Frontend: Broadcast noteUpdated (via WebSocket)
Frontend -> Frontend: Update local state (Redux)

User -> Frontend: Moves note between columns
Frontend -> Router: PUT /boards/{id}/notes/{noteId}/position
Router -> BoardService: moveNote(boardId, noteId, newColumnId)
BoardService -> Database: Update note position
Database --> BoardService: Updated note
BoardService -> Realtime: Publish noteMoved event
Realtime -> Frontend: Broadcast noteMoved (via WebSocket)
Frontend -> Frontend: Update local state (Redux)

@enduml
```